# Uttori Storage Provider - JSON File

Uttori storage provider using JSON files on disk.

## Install

```
$ npm install --save uttori-storage-provider-json-file
```

# Config

```js
{
  content_dir: '',
  history_dir: '',
  data_dir: '',
  extension: 'json',
  spaces_document: null,
  spaces_data: null,
  spaces_history: null,
}
```

